_:N5aceff212611443e9ee92088d07a43c2 <http://schema.org/description> "The Secret Intelligence Service, often known as MI6, collects Britain’s foreign intelligence. It provides the government with a global covert capability to promote and defend the national security and economic well-being of the country. SIS works with the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office ." .
